         1         2         3         4         5         6         7
1234567890123456789012345678901234567890123456789012345678901234567890
======================================================================

                         cvt_dec2string

             Use this function if you want to convert
                 decimal number to ASCII string.

    For example:
        Convert 0x00000007 to 0x00000037
        Convert 0x00000023 to 0x00003332
        Convert 0x00009831 to 0x31333839
        Convert 0x12345678 to 0x3837363534333231

----------------------------------------------------------------------

 DIRECTORY INFORMATION

     doc: Contains documentations about the function.
 example: Some basic tutorials on how to use this function.
     src: Contains source code.
    test: For testing purpose, to ensure the function has no error.

